high_descs: Move close to the little coffee table in front of you, with the open laptop on it.
Pick up the credit card from the coffee table.
Turn left and go to the brown chair with the newspaper on the seat.
Put the credit card on the center front of the seat of the chair.
Turn to face the opposite direction and cross the room to the television screen.
Pick up the credit card that is on the right, under the TV screen.
Turn around and go back to the chair.
Put the credit card directly to the left of the other card on the chair seat.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the seat of a brown chair.

high_descs: Walk to the coffee table in front of you.
Pick up the credit card on the table, to the right of the computer.
Turn to your left and go to the brown arm chair with a newspaper on it.
Place the credit card on the brown arm chair, in front of the newspaper.
Turn around and walk across the room to the television stand.
Pick up the credit card on the right side of the television stand.
Turn around and go back to the brown arm chair across from you.
Place the credit card on the brown arm chair, to the left of the other credit card.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on the brown arm chair.

high_descs: move to the coffee table in the middle of the room
pick up a card from the table
move to the chair to the left of the couch
put the card on the chair
move to the TV stand behind you
pick up a card from the stand
move to the chair to the left of the couch
put the card on the chair
anns.task_desc: Put two cards on a arm chair.
